                            <comment id="434820" author="nscfreny" created="Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:57:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;RHEL 9.5 has been released, kernel updated to 5.14.0-503.11.1.el9_5, b2_15 and b2_16 client builds look ok.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="433905" author="gerrit" created="Tue, 5 Nov 2024 06:30:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&quot; merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/56754/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/56754/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
