                            <comment id="432238" author="yujian" created="Tue, 22 Oct 2024 20:13:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I made Lustre b2_15 client build pass with RHEL kernel 9.5 5.14.0-503.2.1.el9_5. Now pushing the patches to Gerrit. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
